This is a summary of our plans before the next releases:

Release 0.2 : Released 2005-Jan-03



Release 0.3 :
 - Rethink, reorganize, complete the formex transformations
 - Provide short documentation 
 - Change the mouse rotation action  (DONE) 
 - Interface for executing external scripts.
 - Online help system
 - Provide a formian to pyformex translator
 - Add config file and config settings dialog (INITIAL)


Release 0.4 :
  - Better rendering of triangles and polygones.
  - Decent install/uninstall procedures
  - Full manual

Release 0.5 :
  - Multiple views
  - Rendering of externally provided values on the domain.

  
